// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Command menu (inline + reply keyboards)
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// A single source of truth for the user-facing command list. Used to render
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Command handlers (reusable)
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Each handleX(ctx) contains the full body for one command, so it can be
// invoked both from bot.command() (slash command) and from the inline-button
// callback_query dispatcher below. A handler that depends on ctx.match (an
// argument) must gracefully handle the case where ctx.match is undefined —
// that's what happens when triggered from a button.

